The Archer Headboard and Bench Set in Grey has a button tufted design that allows you to create an elegant, yet comfortable, look for your bedroom.  The Archer headboard is thickly padded, tightly upholstered, detailed with deep button tufts, and has elegantly silhouetted wings.  
Complementing the headboard is a matching 52-inch bench upholstered in 100-percent Polyester. The firm, yet comfortable cushioned bench is bordered in a 3/8-inch cording. Both items create stylish additions that tie any bedroom together and work well with a variety of bedding styles letting your decorator style flourish. Comes in Full/Queen headboard, King/California King headboard and bench.
